title: TIP-2:  Formalizing technical agenda
body:
https://gov.thales.io/docs/tip-2

TIP-2 proposes to formalize technical agenda items for Thales.
 The protocol binary option contract suits will go live on Ethereum mainnet enabling users to interact with the Thales smart contract suite.
Launching the minimal viable product, the native token, native token staking, and expanding the Thales systems to Optimism capture the high level technical agenda items for the initial phases Thales will be live.

Are you in favor of this proposal?
